{{#is_warning}}
The FoundationDB log queue is approaching the spill threshold, implying that one or more storage server is struggling to keep up with the workload.
{{/is_warning}}

{{#is_alert}}
The FoundationDB log queue has reached the spill threshold, where logs have not been taken and persisted by storage servers soon enough. This may mean the database workload is more than the cluster can sustain.
{{/is_alert}}
